overview: Gay Frogs, an internet punchline for a many years now, but where did the concept come from? Outside of an Alex Jones rant, where did he get his information? This documentary looks to unsurface the history behind it, talking with Tyrone Hayes who uncovered the whole mystery
tagline: "I have some questions about atrazine, a pesticide." - "Okay" - "Are they putting chemicals in the water to turn the frogs gay?" - "Is this a prank call?" - "No."
title: Gay Frogs: A Deep Dive
